rge.com/2024/7/16/24198753/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-tv-streaming-device-soundbars-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24198753/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-tv-streaming-device-soundbars-sale</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-17T18:03:29-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-17T18:03:29-04:00</updated><title>以下是 Prime Day 最后一天我们最喜欢的科技优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;笔记本电脑和各种其他产品漂浮在星空中的插图，周围环绕着亚马逊箭头。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4xGTZKcqaMsmaOS44HZCRNEzfp8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73465455/247154_Prime_Day_2024_Day_of_Roundup _2_SInbar.0.png&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Shira Inbar for The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;亚马逊的年度销售活动可能即将进入最后一天，但仍有大量耳塞、电视、机器人真空吸尘器和其他珍宝待售大约。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24200040/amazon-prime-day-best-tech-deals-gadgets-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24200040/amazon-prime-day-best-tech-deals-gadgets-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24200040/amazon-prime-day-best-tech-deals-gadgets-2024</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-17T17:48:50-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-17T17:48:50-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊设备上最优惠的 Prime Day 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Kindle Scribe 直立放置在黄色便利贴背景下。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/zZZYCei7Qgm1BJzX4WMWhLEKI8w=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73457589/226417__Amazon_Kindle_Scribe_AKrales_0 197.5.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Kindle Scribe 价格降至历史最低价。&lt;/em>; |图片：Amelia Holowaty Krales&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;mw5UEg&quot;>;2024 年亚马逊 Prime Day 已正式到来。我们已经发布了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24197967/amazon-prime-day-best-tech-deals-gadgets-2024&quot;>;最佳 Prime Day 优惠的详细指南&lt;/ a>;，但如果您只是对亚马逊设备感兴趣，那么您可以在这里找到真正值得的设备。从基于 Alexa 的 Echo 智能扬声器到视频门铃，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/events/devicedeals?discounts-widget=%2522%257B%255C%2522state%255C%2522%253A%257B %255C%2522refinementFilters%255C%2522%253A%257B%257D%257D%252C%255C%2522version%255C%2522%253A1%257D%2522&quot;>;亚马逊正在为各种小工具打折&lt;/a>;，其中一些目前看到的是迄今为止的最低价格。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;BfmcmJ&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;aside:11906226&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div >;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;m8mKVO&quot;>;当然，这里主要需要注意的是，您必须是活跃的 Amazon Prime 会员才能享受所有 Prime Day 优惠。幸运的是，亚马逊&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21493780/amazon-prime-sign-up-day-deals-sale-price-free&quot;>;让注册变得非常容易&lt;/a>; ，特别是新会员可以通过 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/amazonprime/&quot;>;30 天免费试用&lt;/a>;享受独家折扣。&lt;/p>; &lt;div>; &lt;aside id=&quot;iAw8iv&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您可以获得的最佳亚马逊 Prime Day 科技优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24197967/amazon-prime-day-best-tech-deals-gadgets-2024&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;了解以下产品的价格匹配政策百思买、塔吉特、沃尔玛等&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21570383/price-matching-policy-apple-google-microsoft&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt; /aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;h2 id=&quot;kciix7&quot;>;最佳流媒体设备和电视优惠&lt;/h2>; &lt;div id=&quot;OYrDFV&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:12140365&quot;>;&lt;/ div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;div id=&quot;P3RMT1&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:12085801&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;ul>; &lt;li id=&quot;fpt8SS&quot;>;如果您&#39;重新...&lt;/li>; &lt;/ul>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24186875/amazon-prime-day-device-deals-echo-speakers-kindles-fire- tv-streaming-sticks-sale-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24186875/amazon-prime-day-device-deals-echo-speakers-kindles-fire-tv-streaming-sticks-sale-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24186875/amazon-prime-day-device-deals-echo-speakers-kindles-fire-tv-streaming-sticks-sale-2024</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-17T17:20:29-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-17T17:20:29-04:00</updated><title>任天堂为其无线 NES 游戏手柄提供罕见的折扣</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;位于 Nintendo Switch 控制台旁边的无线任天堂娱乐系统控制器。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/5YSrZfwIuNzOs1DdDfnKNMmOTUA=/0x0:1197x798/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73466874/nes_gamepads.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;7 月底之前，购买任天堂复古游戏手柄可节省 12 美元。&lt;/em>; |图片：Nintendo&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;uvLQDg&quot;>;如果您正在寻找一种更真实的方式来创造新的速通记录，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /24199846/nintendo-world-championships-nes-edition-review-switch-speedrunning&quot;>;&lt;em>;任天堂世界锦标赛：NES 版&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;明天推出，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www .nintendo.com/us/store/products/nintendo-entertainment-system-controllers/&quot;>;任天堂现为其无线 NES 游戏手柄提供 20% 的折扣&lt;/a>;，一对的价格从 59.99 美元降至 47.99 美元他们。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ocWYpj&quot;>;促销活动将持续到 7 月 31 日，因此您有几周的时间来享受此次优惠。然而，这些控制器仅适用于拥有付费 Nintendo Switch Online 会员资格的用户，并且免费试用不算在内。您需要使用 Switch 凭据登录&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/nintendo-entertainment-system-controllers/&quot;>;通过 Nintendo 在线商店购买&lt; /a>;，而任天堂是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://en-americas-support.nintendo.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/41222/~/unable-to-place-an-order-for- the-classic-game-controllers-%28nintendo-switch&quot;>;限制销售四套&lt;/a>;两个 NES 控制器。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：任天堂&lt;/a>; cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;无线 NES 游戏手柄...&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17 /24200753/nintendo-deal-gaming-nes-gamepad-controller-wireless&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200753/nintendo-deal-gaming-nes-gamepad-controller-wireless" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24200753/nintendo-deal-gaming-nes-gamepad-controller-wireless</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-17T17:13:48-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-17T17:13:48-04:00</updated><title> 2024 年亚马逊 Prime Day 最佳 Apple 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;木桌上 Apple Smart Folio 中的第 10 代 iPad。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/oYdIb7z8DV-6HI8huMdjGTvSJJg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73463853/226361_Apple_iPad_10.9_10th_gen_ DSeifert_0004.5。 jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;最新款 iPad 价格降至历史最低价。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Dan Seifert / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Q3NbJ3&quot;>;感谢亚马逊 Prime Day，您无需等到今年的黑色星期五即可在苹果产品上节省大笔费用。尽管是亚马逊的活动，但令人惊讶的是，一些最优惠的商品包括流行的苹果产品，从高端 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Apple-Generation-Cancelling-Transparency-Personalized/dp/ B0D1XD1ZV3/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;最新 AirPods Pro&lt;/a>; 到入门级 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp /B0D1WXVQTN/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;第三代 AirPods&lt;/a>; — 两者均创下历史新低价格。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;5zdx1Z&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您可以获得的最佳亚马逊 Prime Day 科技优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24197967/amazon-prime-day-best-tech- Deals-gadgets-2024&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2024 年亚马逊 Prime Day 指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24191617/amazon-prime-day-tech-deals -guide-2024&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/di